{"tid":627372,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[圍讀][讀書App] 召集所有句子迷/鐘意睇書既巴絲打","createTime":"2018-04-13T02:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T02:05:43.000Z","uid":104580,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c89799c274553b9cc7e44977790f5413fc7f78cb","tid":627372,"uid":104580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T02:12:42.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲打睇左好多書,然後好快唔記得晒?<br />\n<br />\n又或者睇完本書都唔明白當中既內容?<br />\n<br />\n有見及此, 小弟係工餘時間同朋友寫左一個 讀書工具既app出黎   名叫【圍讀】<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就係希望讀書唔再孤單,可以透過圍讀平台去分享自己對書睇法,記錄自己鐘意既句子<br />\n<br />\n鐘意睇書既你,不妨花少少時間去嘗試下呢個平台, 記錄留俾手機與電腦，思考留俾大腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n功能介紹<br />\n- 寫下書評、讀後感、筆記<br />\n- 製造書單 收藏不同種類書本<br />\n- 摘下精彩句子<br />\n- 記錄完成閱讀的日期，讀過的書一目了然<br />\n- 查看好友的閱讀記錄<br />\n- 快速連結至圖書館、書店等網頁[製作中]<br />\n<br />\n網址: <a href=\"https://weido.com.tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweido.com.tw&d=kpoCXumN%2Bb2CpWJgotjqcE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=fbcbb27c\" target=\"_blank\">https://weido.com.tw</a><br />\n<br />\nAndroid: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.weido\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.weido&d=kpoCXumN%2Bb2CpWJgotjqcE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=38f2505a\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.weido</a><br />\n<br />\nIOS: <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1353032466\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fapp%2Fid1353032466&d=kpoCXumN%2Bb2CpWJgotjqcE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=fe871bee\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1353032466</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/weido.read/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fweido.read%2F&d=kpoCXumN%2Bb2CpWJgotjqcE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=4df74015\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/weido.read/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔鐘意睇書既你,又想知道下每本書既精華,不妨Like 我地既facebook page, 每日都有唔同既書評推薦"},{"pid":"ca4957caefb2307fba50bb3f2e19ba121584eb5b","tid":627372,"uid":104580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T04:50:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2dc9f5010c20540ed371fe11a21efa563211887","tid":627372,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:26:49.000Z","msg":"研究吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a5230a88c485c24053c77118b75fe6355af782","tid":627372,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:15:28.000Z","msg":"留明 我用緊樊登讀書會"},{"pid":"810f6e1fee012e94cf8b1acdceaf7403648b235a","tid":627372,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:55:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21ca93bf24161f598e1aeb424a6490ff725d8707","tid":627372,"uid":104580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c5a5230a88c485c24053c77118b75fe6355af782","tid":627372,"uid":71160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:15:28.000Z","msg":"留明 我用緊樊登讀書會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T07:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地網站搞緊活動<br />\n送kindle 閱讀器/自選圖片<br />\n有興趣上我地官網睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://weido.com.tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweido.com.tw&d=kpoCXumN%2Bb2CpWJgotjqcE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=fbcbb27c\" target=\"_blank\">https://weido.com.tw</a>"},{"pid":"a620de3cd7ac4885a0341f5c90deeaf83b472a9e","tid":627372,"uid":104580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T11:49:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d0095c6ca1aad928485b634247a9454db9780cb","tid":627372,"uid":104580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T15:27:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a26fc146160ef98c6a4c6d76d837592880b51eec","tid":627372,"uid":116967,"like":0,"dislike":0